### Youyu - Full Admin Flow Seed Walkthrough
### Start backend with seed profile before running:
### backend\mvnw.cmd spring-boot:run "-Dspring-boot.run.arguments=--spring.profiles.active=seed"
### IDE program argument: --spring.profiles.active=seed

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken = mock-9001-ADMIN
@superAdminToken = mock-9101-SUPER_ADMIN
@supportToken = mock-9102-SUPPORT_AGENT
@reviewerToken = mock-9103-REVIEWER
@operatorToken = mock-9104-OPERATOR
@orderAdminToken = mock-9105-ORDER_ADMIN

### 0. Seed login smoke: super admin account should exist in the active database.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "superadmin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 0b. Seed login smoke: specialist reviewer account should exist in the active database.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "reviewer",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 1. Super admin dashboard should show live queues.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}

### 2. Reviewer checks pending student verification seed records.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/verifications?status=pending_review&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{reviewerToken}}

### 3. Reviewer checks pending product review tasks.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/review-tasks?status=pending_review&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{reviewerToken}}

### 4. Reviewer checks pending shop admission.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/shops?reviewStatus=pending_review&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{reviewerToken}}

### 5. Support agent reviews pending and processing reports.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}

### 6. Order admin reviews seeded order queues.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{orderAdminToken}}

### 7. Support agent opens active mediation case with order and chat context.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/mediation-cases/70001
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}

### 8. Super admin reviews resolved mediation decision path.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/mediation-cases/70002
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}

### 9. Operator reviews search governance rules and logs.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/search/governance-rules
Authorization: Bearer {{operatorToken}}

### 10. Super admin reviews seeded audit trail examples.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/audit-logs?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}

### 11. Permission smoke: reviewer cannot access admin orders.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{reviewerToken}}

### 12. Permission smoke: support agent cannot make final mediation decision.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/mediation-cases/70001/decision
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "decisionCategory": "order_completion_required",
  "decisionSummary": "Permission smoke should be rejected."
}
